{
  "stem": "18486.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 472.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And his son lives with us here in Woodstock.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, they crawled.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They could sit.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But there were lines, flashlights.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, it was good that there was no radio, because they would have heard it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was not that deep.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And one day, this director from the blast furnaces-- he was such a strange guy.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was a very nice man.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he was not Jewish, but they sought him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so when he got-- went in that tunnel, he stayed in the entrance instead of going deeper in.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, of course, I didn't know that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then the Germans came, and I always was standing near that entrance.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I prefer to stand on it, so that I somehow, you know?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then I heard-- certainly heard [WHISTLING].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was whistling.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Oh, God.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the Germans were standing there with me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I did-- I suddenly stood up where I was standing-- You can't go away!",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You can't go away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I can't go away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I did so-- [CLAPS] And I said, I'm so cold!",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm so cold! here!",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was not cold at all.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But he fell for it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he heard me trampling, and so he stopped whistling.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He suddenly realized what he was doing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 129,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But that was one of the narrow escapes.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
